title: Two Guys Smoke Shop 28th Anniversary PARTY!
itunes:title: Two Guys Smoke Shop 28th Anniversary PARTY!
description: Live from an undisclosed location, it's Two guys Smoke Shop's 28th Anniversary... and we're giving away a DeLorean! We've got the who's-who of Cigarlebrities including JR Dominguez and Scott Weeks from Recluse Cigars, Cristian Eiora from CLE and Eiora Cigars, David Topper from Alec Bradley Cigars, Ernesto Perez Carrillo from EPC Cigars, Patric Hurd from the new Pysco Seven Cigars, Nick Perdomo from Perdomo Cigars, Tom Ryhiner from Davidoff Cigars, Tom Lazuka from Asylum Cigars, Litto Comez from La Flor Dominicana, Nelson Alfonso from Atabey, Byron and the new Bandolero Cigars, Eric Newman from Diamond Crown Cigars, amd David Laffery from CYB Cigars.
